1. Danas sam platio duplo više za ovaj novi telefon. (*duplo*) (Today I paid twice as much for this new phone.)
2. Vežbao sam duplo više nego obično. (*duplo*) (I practiced twice as much as usual.)
3. Duplo sam provjerio prije nego što sam poslao mejl. (*duplo*) (I double-checked before sending the email.)
4. Rekao sam joj da će ono što joj nudim biti duplo bolje od konkurencije. (*duplo*) (I told her that what I offer will be twice as good as the competition.)
5. Moje radno vrijeme je duplo kraće od tvog. (*duplo*) (My working hours are half as long as yours.)
6. Volim kada mi daju duplo karamelne bombone. (*duplo*) (I love when they give me double caramel candies.)
7. Sutra ću biti duplo bolje pripremljen za sastanak. (*duplo*) (Tomorrow I'll be twice as well prepared for the meeting.)
8. On je duplo stariji od nje. (*duplo*) (He's twice as old as her.)
9. Ova torta ima duplo više šlaga nego prošle godine. (*duplo*) (This cake has twice as much whipped cream as last year.)
10. Duplo mjerilo je potrebno za ovaj projekt. (*duplo*) (We need a double measuring tape for this project.)